"/></inline-formula>相等，记为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>2) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>小于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，记为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>3) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>大于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，记为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>定义三( [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19734-ref18">18</xref>] ): 设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为一组直觉模糊数，且设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，若</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19734-formula39"><label>(1)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x55_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>则称<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>维直觉模糊加权平均算子，其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x58_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的权重向量，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>定义四( [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19734-ref19">19</xref>] ): 设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为一组直觉模糊数，且设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，若</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19734-formula40"><label>(2)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-1170144x64_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><table-wrap id="table1" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table1">Table 1</xref></label><caption><title> The evaluation index system of enterprise marketing competition priority intangible facto</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >一级指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >二级指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >三级指标</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="19"  >制造企业市场营销竞争优先权无形要素总评价值</td><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="4"  >可持续、开放、共享营销理念(X1)</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >品牌产品销售比率(Y1)</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >企业环境信用等级(Y2)</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >出口产品销售比上升率(Y3)</td></tr><tr><td al